snippet.title: TOASTERBALL - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
TOASTERBALL is leaving early access on May 3rd, on PC (Switch version coming soon!)

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1142810/Toasterball/

🌍 New maps
🤖 New AI
🛠 New custom mode

And many more surprises!
